'''''Man in die Donker''''' ('''Man in the Dark'''), ni filime yo mu 1962 yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo y'Abirabura n'abazungu Neo-noir iyobowe na Truida Louw Pohl ikaba yarayikoranye na Aletta Gericke<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2180469/</ref>, Truida Louw na Renée van der Walt kuri Trio-Films<ref>https://esat.sun.ac.za/index.php/Trio_Films</ref>.  Iyi niyo filime yambere yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo iyobowe numugore mumateka ya sinema yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/The_Great_Kimberley_Diamond_Robbery</ref>.  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Babs Laker na Dawid van der Walt mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Cor Nortjé, Mathilde Hanekom na Elsa Fouché mu nshingano zabo.<ref>https://www.goldposter.com/movie/10341434/</ref> 

